lyrics:
being sick for a week

[Verse]
Gotta fever burning, feeling weak all day
Lost my voice, but I'm ready to slay
Pounding headache, can't catch a break
Been sick for a week, need an antidote, for goodness sake

[Chorus]
Sick, sick, sick, but I won't quit
Gonna fight through, won't let it hit
Body aching, but my spirit's high
I'm a glitched-out pop star, this won't pass me by
